children.text: The diagonal speedbracing that runs across the tops of the trusses has not been properly fixed to the heels of the cantilever trusses.

The relevant Australian Standard, AS 4440 Installation of Nail-Plated Timber Roof Trusses, clause 4.3.8 Fixing, provides a detail outlining the method for connecting speedbrace to the heel of cantilever trusses;
The fixing of the speedbracing must be rectified in accordance with Australian Standard AS 4440, to ensure the performance of the roof bracing system.
